_Sum(n):\n    # Using the formula for the sum of fifth powers of first n natural numbers:\n    # sum(k=1 to n) k^5 = (n^2 * (n+1)^2 * (2n^2 + 2n - 1)) // 12\n    return (n**2 * (n+1)**2 * (2*n**2 + 2*n - 1)) // 12\n\n# Assertions to verify the function\nassert fifth_Power_Sum(2) == 33\nassert fifth_Power_Sum(4) == 1300\nassert fifth_Power_Sum(3) == 276"}
